// One.js

import React from 'react';
import { Container, Typography, Card, CardContent, Grid, Link } from '@mui/material';
import { OpenInNew as OpenInNewIcon } from '@mui/icons-material';
import './one.css';

const One = () => {
  return (
    <Container className="one-container">
      <header>
        <Typography variant="h4">Action Research Studies: Instructional Strategies</Typography>
        <Typography variant="subtitle1">Uncovering impactful student-centered instructional methods and diverse learning strategies</Typography>
      </header>

      <section className="video-section">
        <iframe
          title="Canva Video Presentation"
          width="100%"
          height="400"
          src="https://www.canva.com/design/DAF1wj4fUqo/73VP3AthaztrTP5OlQz1Kvw/watch?utm_content=DAF1wj4fUqo&utm_campaign=share_your_design&utm_medium=link&utm_source=shareyourdesignpanel"
          allowFullScreen
        />
      </section>

      <section className="summary-section">
        <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom>
          Research Findings Summary
        </Typography>
        <Typography paragraph>
          The research findings indicate a strong correlation between student engagement and the implementation of student-centered instructional methods. The Universal Design for Learning strategy emerged as a versatile approach, catering to diverse learning needs.
        </Typography>
        <Typography paragraph>
          Educators are encouraged to leverage the insights from this study to enhance their teaching practices and create inclusive, engaging learning environments.
        </Typography>
      </section>

      <section className="related-section">
        <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom>
          Related Articles and Resources
        </Typography>
        <Grid container spacing={3}>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
            <Card>
              <CardContent>
                <Typography variant="h6">Article 1</Typography>
                <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                  Explore more about effective classroom management techniques and strategies.
                </Typography>
                <Link href="/article-1" underline="none" target="_blank">
                  Read More <OpenInNewIcon fontSize="small" />
                </Link>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
            <Card>
              <CardContent>
                <Typography variant="h6">Article 2</Typography>
                <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                  Learn how to develop impactful lesson plans that foster student engagement.
                </Typography>
                <Link href="/article-2" underline="none" target="_blank">
                  Read More <OpenInNewIcon fontSize="small" />
                </Link>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
            <Card>
              <CardContent>
                <Typography variant="h6">Resource 1</Typography>
                <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                  Access additional tools and resources for inclusive teaching practices.
                </Typography>
                <Link href="/resource-1" underline="none" target="_blank">
                  Explore <OpenInNewIcon fontSize="small" />
                </Link>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </section>
    </Container>
  );
}

export default One;
